What_is_your_return_policy_reply: If you're not satisfied with your purchase, we accept returns within 30 days of delivery. To initiate a return, please email us at support@myecommercestore.com with your order number and a brief explanation of why you're returning the item.
How_do_I_track_my_order_reply: You can track your order by clicking the tracking link in your shipping confirmation email, or by logging into your account on our website and viewing the order details.
How_do_I_contact_customer_support_reply: You can contact our customer support team by emailing us at support@myecommercestore.com, or by calling us at (555) 123-4567 between the hours of 9am and 5pm EST, Monday through Friday.
Can_I_change_or_cancel_my_order_reply: Unfortunately, once an order has been placed, we are not able to make changes or cancellations. If you no longer want the items you've ordered, you can return them for a refund within 30 days of delivery.
Do_you_offer_international_shipping_repl: Currently, we only offer shipping within the United States.
What_payment_methods_do_you_accept_reply: We accept visa,mastercard,paypal payment method also we have cash on delivery system.
